Name: cedar creek lake, texas
Description: the laek my family and i go to every year, it's got the best swimming, tubbing, boating and sunsets in the world

Name: american airlines hockey rink located in dallas texas
Description: a pace i have been going to since i was 2 months old, my family and i are die hard dallas stars hockey fans, i love dallas but wanted a specific point in dallas! a great place to watch a game with friends or family and see some pretty cool hockey players!

Name: victoria falls, zimbabwe
Description: one of the coolest places i have ever been too. i still remember to this day standing on an outlook and feeling the msit of the falls and the river hitting my cheeks and nose.

Name: cape code, massachusetts
Description: the last place my family and i traveled too. has some of the best memories with my family from touring the sand dunes in provincetown, to biking around nantucket island.

Name: grand canyon, arizona
Description: this place has always been on my bucket list and I went for the first time with my mom and uncle over this summer as we drove my car over here. I remember waking up to the canyon on the southern end of the south rim trail, t had just rained and i kid you not a double rainbow went over and through the canyon the first time i saw the canyon.
